OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCourt says Trump can be    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsued for Capitol riot      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A federal appeals court has ruled that 
OL,6, Donald Trump can be sued in civil court
OL,7, for his role in allegedly inciting the 
OL,8, riot on Capitol Hill in January 2021.  
OL,10,FIt comes after two injured Capitol     
OL,11,FPolice officers sued Mr Trump for      
OL,12,Ftelling the crowd to "fight like hell" 
OL,13,Fshortly before the violence began.     
OL,15,FMr Trump had sought to claim immunity  
OL,16,Fstemming from his role as president.   
OL,18,FBut the three-judge panel found that Mr
OL,19,FTrump was not acting in an official    
OL,20,Frole when he made the remarks.         
